CSS :

1. Full form of css is Cascading stylesheet.
2. CSS was developed by W3C world wide web consortium under Hakum wium lie. 
3. CSS is mainly used to make web page more effective and attractive
4. Css provides various ways to implement colors in our website
5. Css provides several units for implementing in websites 
6. There are three ways to implement CSS : 
    a. Inline CSS
    b. Internal CSS 
    c. External CSS

    Out of this three css, priority goes to inline css and recomended approach to use css is external css

7. Css provides the concept of media query to make web page responsive.

8. Css provides the concept of animation, flex box, transition  and grid system to make web page more attractive

9. Css is dependent upon HTML